        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 13 at 1:56PM MDT until June 13 at 2:15PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 156 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 20 miles east of
Toston, or 26 miles southeast of Townsend, moving east at 35 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
southeastern Broadwater, south central Meagher and northeastern
Gallatin Counties.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
